mm/debug: Add VM_BUG_ON_FOLIO() and VM_WARN_ON_ONCE_FOLIO()

These are the folio equivalents of VM_BUG_ON_PAGE and
VM_WARN_ON_ONCE_PAGE.  No change to generated code.

